{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.1","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:1","prev_osis_id":"Heb.013.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Adresse et salutation<\/h3>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Jacques, serviteur de Dieu et du Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ, aux douze tribus qui sont dans la dispersion, salut!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.2","name":"Jacques 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.13.25","name":"H\u00e9breux 13:25","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.13.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.2","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:2","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.003,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les \u00e9preuves et les tentations<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 2-8: cf. (Ro 5:3-5. Ja 5:7-11.) (Mt 7:7-11. Mc 11:24. H\u00e9 11:6.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>\n    Mes fr\u00e8res, regardez comme un sujet de joie compl\u00e8te les diverses \u00e9preuves auxquelles vous pouvez \u00eatre expos\u00e9s,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.3","name":"Jacques 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.1","name":"Jacques 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.3","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:3","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>sachant que l\u2019\u00e9preuve de votre foi produit la patience.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.4","name":"Jacques 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.2","name":"Jacques 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.4","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:4","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Mais il faut que la patience accomplisse parfaitement son \u0153uvre, afin que vous soyez parfaits et accomplis, sans faillir en rien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.5","name":"Jacques 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.3","name":"Jacques 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.5","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:5","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Si quelqu\u2019un d\u2019entre vous manque de sagesse, qu\u2019il la demande \u00e0 Dieu, qui donne \u00e0 tous simplement et sans reproche, et elle lui sera donn\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.6","name":"Jacques 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.4","name":"Jacques 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.6","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:6","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Mais qu\u2019il la demande avec foi, sans douter; car celui qui doute est semblable au flot de la mer, agit\u00e9 par le vent et pouss\u00e9 de c\u00f4t\u00e9 et d\u2019autre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.7","name":"Jacques 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.5","name":"Jacques 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.7","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:7","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Qu\u2019un tel homme ne s\u2019imagine pas qu\u2019il recevra quelque chose du Seigneur:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.8","name":"Jacques 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.6","name":"Jacques 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.8","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:8","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>c\u2019est un homme irr\u00e9solu, inconstant dans toutes ses voies.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.9","name":"Jacques 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.7","name":"Jacques 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.9","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:9","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-12: cf. J\u00e9 9:23, 24. \u00c9z 7:19. Ap 2:10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Que le fr\u00e8re de condition humble se glorifie de son \u00e9l\u00e9vation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.10","name":"Jacques 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.8","name":"Jacques 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.10","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:10","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Que le riche, au contraire, se glorifie de son humiliation; car il passera comme la fleur de l\u2019herbe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.11","name":"Jacques 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.9","name":"Jacques 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.11","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:11","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Le soleil s\u2019est lev\u00e9 avec sa chaleur ardente, il a dess\u00e9ch\u00e9 l\u2019herbe, sa fleur est tomb\u00e9e, et la beaut\u00e9 de son aspect a disparu: ainsi le riche se fl\u00e9trira dans ses entreprises.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.12","name":"Jacques 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.10","name":"Jacques 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.12","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:12","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Heureux l\u2019homme qui supporte patiemment la tentation; car, apr\u00e8s avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 \u00e9prouv\u00e9, il recevra la couronne de vie, que le Seigneur a promise \u00e0 ceux qui l\u2019aiment.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.13","name":"Jacques 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.11","name":"Jacques 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.13","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:13","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-15: cf. Ge 3:6, etc.; 4:7.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Que personne, lorsqu\u2019il est tent\u00e9, ne dise: C\u2019est Dieu qui me tente. Car Dieu ne peut \u00eatre tent\u00e9 par le mal, et il ne tente lui-m\u00eame personne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.14","name":"Jacques 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.12","name":"Jacques 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.14","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:14","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Mais chacun est tent\u00e9 quand il est attir\u00e9 et amorc\u00e9 par sa propre convoitise.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.15","name":"Jacques 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.13","name":"Jacques 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.15","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:15","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Puis la convoitise, lorsqu\u2019elle a con\u00e7u, enfante le p\u00e9ch\u00e9; et le p\u00e9ch\u00e9, \u00e9tant consomm\u00e9, produit la mort.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.16","name":"Jacques 1:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.14","name":"Jacques 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.16","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:16","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.017,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Mettre en pratique la parole de Dieu<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 16-27: cf. Jn 3:27. 1 Pi 1:23-25; 2:1, 2. (Mt 7:21-27. Ga 6:7-10.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Ne vous y trompez pas, mes fr\u00e8res bien-aim\u00e9s:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.17","name":"Jacques 1:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.15","name":"Jacques 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.17","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:17","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>toute gr\u00e2ce excellente et tout don parfait descendent d\u2019en haut, du P\u00e8re des lumi\u00e8res, chez lequel il n\u2019y a ni changement ni ombre de variation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.18","name":"Jacques 1:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.16","name":"Jacques 1:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.18","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:18","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Il nous a engendr\u00e9s selon sa volont\u00e9, par la parole de v\u00e9rit\u00e9, afin que nous soyons en quelque sorte les pr\u00e9mices de ses cr\u00e9atures.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.19","name":"Jacques 1:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.17","name":"Jacques 1:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.19","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:19","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Sachez-le, mes fr\u00e8res bien-aim\u00e9s. Ainsi, que tout homme soit prompt \u00e0 \u00e9couter, lent \u00e0 parler, lent \u00e0 se mettre en col\u00e8re;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.20","name":"Jacques 1:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.18","name":"Jacques 1:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.20","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:20","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>car la col\u00e8re de l\u2019homme n\u2019accomplit pas la justice de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.21","name":"Jacques 1:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.19","name":"Jacques 1:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.21","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:21","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi, rejetant toute souillure et tout exc\u00e8s de malice, recevez avec douceur la parole qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 plant\u00e9e en vous, et qui peut sauver vos \u00e2mes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.22","name":"Jacques 1:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.20","name":"Jacques 1:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.22","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:22","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Mettez en pratique la parole, et ne vous bornez pas \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9couter, en vous trompant vous-m\u00eames par de faux raisonnements.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.23","name":"Jacques 1:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.21","name":"Jacques 1:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.23","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:23","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Car, si quelqu\u2019un \u00e9coute la parole et ne la met pas en pratique, il est semblable \u00e0 un homme qui regarde dans un miroir son visage naturel,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.24","name":"Jacques 1:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.22","name":"Jacques 1:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.24","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:24","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>et qui, apr\u00e8s s\u2019\u00eatre regard\u00e9, s\u2019en va, et oublie aussit\u00f4t quel il \u00e9tait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.25","name":"Jacques 1:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.23","name":"Jacques 1:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.25","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:25","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Mais celui qui aura plong\u00e9 les regards dans la loi parfaite, la loi de la libert\u00e9, et qui aura pers\u00e9v\u00e9r\u00e9, n\u2019\u00e9tant pas un auditeur oublieux, mais se mettant \u00e0 l\u2019\u0153uvre, celui-l\u00e0 sera heureux dans son activit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.26","name":"Jacques 1:26","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.24","name":"Jacques 1:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.26","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:26","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.001.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Si quelqu\u2019un croit \u00eatre religieux, sans tenir sa langue en bride, mais en trompant son c\u0153ur, la religion de cet homme est vaine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.27","name":"Jacques 1:27","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.25","name":"Jacques 1:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.27","label":"","reference":"Jacques 1:27","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.1.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>La religion pure et sans tache, devant Dieu notre P\u00e8re, consiste \u00e0 visiter les orphelins et les veuves dans leurs afflictions, et \u00e0 se pr\u00e9server des souillures du monde.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.1","name":"Jacques 1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.1","name":"Jacques 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.26","name":"Jacques 1:26","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbe3ae1b6.02963894');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbe3ae1b6.02963894\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbe3ae1b6.02963894","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbe3ae1b6.02963894'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbe3ae1b6.02963894\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}